{"id":319507,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/10/维权网-成都西部博览会拒绝访民参加，多人/","date":"2013-10-24T08:17:26Z","modified":"2013-10-24T08:17:26Z","title":"维权网 | 成都“西部博览会”拒绝访民参加，多人被限制人身自由（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span><br /></span></p>\n<div><span>（维权网信息员向云报道）</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">23</span><span>号上午，成都市青白江访民林德琼、王于英，金牛区彭天惠，新津谢志勇、张晓兰等人到新会展中心参观西博会，然正在参观过程中，林德琼、王于英、谢志勇、彭天惠、张晓兰及后来的幸素芳、盛素芬、赵双秀等成都访民就被警察拦截，强制传唤到新会展中心派出所，在做完笔录后被当地维稳人员强制接回家看守。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>     </span></span></div>\n<div><span>据悉，在</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日下午</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2:30</span><span>时，成都青羊区强拆访民王蓉文刚下楼，就被街道办截住，带上车，说出去“旅游”两天。她报警</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">110</span><span>，黄瓦街派出所出警在斌升街</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>号找到她后，反而说要她配合非法限制她人身自由的维稳人员。随后她被看守在家，不让她参加“西部博览会”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>     </span></span></div>\n<div><span>同样，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">22</span><span>日，成都锦江区强拆访民邓品芳，也被政府维稳人员非法拘禁在家，不让她参加“西部博览会”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>     </span></span></div>\n<div><span>在这之前的</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日，曾绍梅、陈伦珍、李廷惠、周成群进京上访被截回成都，刚下火车就被各地政府强制带走“旅游”。曾绍梅被接回后，由维稳人员跟踪监控中，她们都被拒绝参加“西部博览会”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>     </span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日，成都市青白江大同镇五里村</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">11</span><span>组王于英，因成都西部博览会政府开始派</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">4-5</span><span>人看守她。同日，锦江区访民邓晓英也接到电话通知她，</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">21</span><span>日到街道办维稳谈话。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>     </span></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日，成都锦江强拆访民郭玉彬，今日下午被四名维稳人员强制带到重庆“旅游”。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>     </span></span></div>\n<div><span>更多的访民被拒绝参加“西部博览会”尚在统计中，而那些悄无声息被维稳拒绝参加“西部博览会”的访民只有等</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">10</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">27</span><span>日结束后才能得知。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-FQK4-sJqhYs/Umino6zXyPI/AAAAAAAAp5w/bqGWOrf8SXk/s1600/980330CD-86AA-4B77-98C2-2DBF215C0E43.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"180\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-FQK4-sJqhYs/Umino6zXyPI/AAAAAAAAp5w/bqGWOrf8SXk/s320/980330CD-86AA-4B77-98C2-2DBF215C0E43.jpg\" width=\"320\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910,19196]}